{"tid":2092212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"名AV女優遭情色龍頭壓榨讓人心疼　逾150萬網友請願下架影片","createTime":"2020-07-03T06:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T07:06:32.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8b900b944e77c0f923867cdaaac11a4161bcea2f","tid":2092212,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/2q02OVaPGSQlMIIVw3hqu8gltMs=/760x570/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/73NRLK2WIDHULSJVHQ7VNXZ5IY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2q02OVaPGSQlMIIVw3hqu8gltMs%3D%2F760x570%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F73NRLK2WIDHULSJVHQ7VNXZ5IY.jpg&h=606f1009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n名AV女優卡莉法遭情色龍頭壓榨讓人心疼，逾150萬網友請願下架影片<br />\n<br />\n曾被喻為「世界第一AV女優」的美國女星卡莉法(Mia Khalifa)，雖然現在已經退出AV界，但過去她以低廉價格拍攝的A片，迄今仍在情色龍頭網站「Pornhub」不斷播映，更流傳至其他網站。卡莉法過去曾表示，對這樣的狀況感到無奈，已經做好心理準備，讓這些「A片魔咒」跟著她一輩子，但有不少民眾心疼卡莉法的遭遇，最新消息指出，有超過150萬民眾到「<a href=\"http://Change.Org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FChange.Org&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=51a6f059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Change.Org</a>」請願，下架以卡莉法為名的所有A片。<br />\n<br />\n卡莉法在2014年曾經短暫當過3個月的AV女優，當時她年僅21歲，她一共拍過12部片，更一躍成為點閱率最高的AV女優，不過她片酬共只有12000美元(約新台幣36萬元)。之後卡莉法離開AV界，但這些片子不斷在Pornhub上「重播」，情色網站和製作公司獲取更大利潤。卡莉法先前接受英國《BBC》訪問時承認，雖然她紅了，但帶給她更多羞恥感，現在上網一查她的名字，就跟AV脫離不了關係。<br />\n<br />\n卡莉法一度爭取要從網站移除自己的影片，但目前仍然困難，她也曾說：「做好被A片跟一輩子的準備。」有不少網友心疼卡莉法的遭遇，在「<a href=\"http://Change.Org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FChange.Org&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=51a6f059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Change.Org</a>」發起請願，指控當年的AV製作公司「BangBros」不斷將6年的舊片重新包裝，再重新出版上傳，讓不知情者以為是新片，進而點閱，而製作公司與情色網站即能因此得利。據英國《衛報》與《都市報》等報導，目前已有超過150萬網友連署支持，要求網站與製作公司下架卡莉法的色情片"},{"pid":"abc4c648f3601a66b805baaf84170a9546ecb819","tid":2092212,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾post <br />\n拉</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b5ae8ff2fcbc617c285271ff469c2bef39b210db","tid":2092212,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"又做雞又要排方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9170b009218c39ee25137474a21fc65a42ee3efa","tid":2092212,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"其實d人可以送一筆錢比佢未得<br />\n<br />\n做雞點解要拎貞節牌坊？"},{"pid":"802452a83993401894b37aac1da5d014e78b660f","tid":2092212,"uid":103218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"早幾日先翻睇佢戴住穆斯林頭巾含撚條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbee0cbbd138d4cc9939083144261e9a66a56c8","tid":2092212,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ae8ff2fcbc617c285271ff469c2bef39b210db","tid":2092212,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"又做雞又要排方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"呢條片有講原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G-zwsDGW5NU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG-zwsDGW5NU&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=d17d17d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G-zwsDGW5NU</a>"},{"pid":"ae4a0e7058f9d0986e44b527bb8a0a96209c2166","tid":2092212,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802452a83993401894b37aac1da5d014e78b660f","tid":2092212,"uid":103218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"早幾日先翻睇佢戴住穆斯林頭巾含撚條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T0